    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund work on pavements to make them more disabled friendly",
        "additional_details": "I\u2019ve just started using a mobility scooter and the pavements can be awful. Some aren\u2019t straight and 1 curb in my area is so uneven it goes into a point. I think many are unsafe for any wheelchair or mobility scooter users and I think we need to have drop curbs on every junction.",
        "background": "I want the government to provide funding to have pavements resurfaced so they are more disability friendly. I think the state of pavements amounts to disability discrimination.",
